lead_paragraph: England's Justin Rose left his gold medal from the Rio Olympics home, needing no further inspiration this week than the chance to win another Ryder Cup for Europe.

headline.print_headline: Rose Leaves Olympic Gold Medal Home to Focus on Gold Trophy
